  <summary date="2017-01-04T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Medicare Prescription Drug Price Negotiation Act of 2017

This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to require the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS) to negotiate with pharmaceutical companies regarding&#160;prices for drugs covered&#160;under the Medicare prescription drug benefit. Current law prohibits CMS from doing so.</summary>
